data.description: Charming brick ranch in Mishawaka! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on a double lot at the corner of Division and La Salle. With a fenced backyard and 20 years of love, it's ready for a new owner to add their personal touch. While the basement is not finished, offers great potential. TLC and some updating will make it even more cozy. Has living room, eat in kitchen and 2 car garage. New furnace and A/C in 2023. There is a bathroom in the lower level that needs a new wax ring and some updating, sellers are not using. Also, a newer water softener but not hooked up. The home was "overbuilt" by the builder with larger foundation under concrete block wall basement. Tornado straps from roof to foundation. Floor trusses housing all utilities covered by a drop-tile ceiling in the basement. Don't miss out ! Schedule a showing today!
